  <thing id="iLaerStmAr" name="Laeral&#146;s Storm Armor" description="This +2 fire and lightning resistance full plate armor is made of a nonmetallic material (rumored to be native to another plane) that does not conduct electricity. The \nwearer is never hindered or moved against her will by strong winds.\n\nCaster Level: 6th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}gust of wind{/i}, {i}resist elements{/i}, creator must be at least 6th level; Market Price: 66,650 gp; Cost to Create: 34,150 gp + 2,600 XP.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Magic of Faer&#251;n{/i}, 3.0 Edition" compset="MagicArmor" summary="Absorbs first 10pts of Fire or Lightning damage.  Unhindered by wind.">
