  <thing id="iArrowBite" name="Arrow of Biting" description="This arrow injects poison (Fort DC 16, 1d10 Con/1d10 Con) into its target. If the projectile misses, it is destroyed. Arrows of biting are manufactured individually, not in lots of fifty as with other projectiles.\nThey are sometimes crafted as crossbow bolts or javelins.\nCaster Level: 7th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, poison; Market Price: 1,457 gp; Cost to Create: 732 gp + 58 XP.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Magic of Faer&#251;n{/i}, 3.0 Edition" compset="MagicWep" summary="Injects Poison (DC 16) 1d10 Con/1d10 Con.">
