  <thing id="iBlingWarp" name="Blingdenstone Warpick" description="While many of these +1 corrosive heavy picks are in the hands of the homeless deep gnomes living in the Silver Marches, some have begun to circulate because of adventurers who have looted the drow infested city of Blingdenstone.\nCaster Level: 10th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}acid fog{/i}, {i}acid storm{/i}, {i}Melf&#146;s acid arrow{/i}, or {i}storm of vengeance{/i}; Market Price: 8,308 gp; Cost to Create: 4,308 gp + 320 XP.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Magic of Faer&#251;n{/i}, 3.0 Edition" compset="MagicWep" summary="+1d6 Acid damage on each hit.">
