  <thing id="iCormyrGob" name="Cormyrian Goblinthrasher" description="These +1 goblinoid bane longswords are adorned with the rampant purple dragon symbol of Cormyr. Royal Magician Caladnei has commissioned the War Wizards to create many of these weapons for distribution among the Purple Dragon knights and general sale, in order to generate revenue for the country and improve morale. The ones awarded to the knights are typically inscribed with marks of honor and distinction appropriate to the recipient.\n\nCaster Level: 8th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}summon monster I{/i}; Market Price: 18,315 gp; Cost to Create: 9,315 gp + 720 XP.\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Magic of Faer&#251;n{/i}, 3.0 Edition" compset="MagicWep" summary="+1 Goblinoid Bane weapons for the Purple Dragon Knights.">
