  <thing id="iJusticeBl" name="Justice Blade" description="The church of Torm has manufactured many of these +1 holy mighty cleaving longswords. Seemingly made of magically hardened bronze and inscribed with the hammer and scales symbol of Tyr, a justice blade always sheds pure white light in a 20-foot radius when drawn.\n\nCaster Level: 8th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}divine power{/i}, {i}holy smite{/i}, creator must be good; Market Price: 32,315 gp; Cost to Create: 16,315 gp + 1,280 XP.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Magic to Faer&#251;n{/i}, 3.0 Edition" compset="MagicWep" summary="+1 Extra Cleave per round; +2d6 vs Evil creatures.">
