  <thing id="iLuirShtBo" name="Luiren Shortbow" description="These +1 seeking shortbows have become well known in the northern lands because of the many Luiren halflings bearing them. Some of them have been sold by down-on-their-luck kin and become prized by other folk.\n\nCaster Level: 10th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}keen edge{/i}; Market Price: 8,330 gp; Cost to Create: 4,330 gp + 320 XP.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Magic to Faer&#251;n{/i}, 3.0 Edition" compset="MagicWep" summary="+1 Seeking Shortbow (negates miss chance from concealment)">
