  <thing id="iSilvermaA" name="Silvermane&#146;s Axe" description="This +3 evil outsider bane battleaxe is inscribed with the symbol of Moradin and a phrase in dwarven: &#147;Let the fiends fall before me, to the greatest glory of my clan, as I stand upon their heaped corpses and bellow the Soul Forger&#146;s name.&#148;\n\nCaster Level: 8th; Prerequisite: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}summon monster I{/i}, creator must be a dwarf and at least 9th level; Market Price: 50,302 gp; Cost to Create: 25,302 gp + 2,000 XP.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Magic to Faer&#251;n{/i}, 3.0 Edition" compset="MagicWep" summary="+3 Evil Outsider Bane Battlaxe">
    <comment>Not sure its working...</comment>
