  <thing id="ioMooncl3" name="Mooncloak, +3" description="Mooncloak: This silvery-gray cloak is one of the items typically created by Sel&#251;ne&#146;s moonfire, but has since been duplicated by spellcasters. The cloak functions as a cloak of resistance, plus gives the wearer the ability to levitate and water walk (both self only) once per day.\n\nCaster Level: 7th; Prerequisites: Craft Wondrous Item, {i}levitate{/i}, {i}resistance{/i}, {i}water walk{/i}, creator&#146;s levelmust be three times that of the cloak&#146;s bonus (mimumum 7th level); Market Price: 18,800 gp (+3); Weight: 1 lb.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Magic to Faer&#251;n{/i}, 3.0 Edition" compset="Wondrous" summary="+3 Saves; 1/Day (each) (self-only) levitate and water walk">
