  <thing id="cWWcBonMM2" name="Bonus Metamagic" description="War wizards focus their studies of spellcasting efficiency. In order to achieve that end, they develop expertise in a variety of metamagic techniques. At 2nd level and again at 4th level, the war wizard gains a bonus metamagic feat of her choice to add to her repertoire of knowledge." compset="ClSpecial">
