  <thing id="sWizNyWrCa" name="Nybor&apos;s Wrathful Castigation" description="{i}Nybor&apos;s wrathful castigation{/i} is an even more potent version of {i}Nybor&apos;s stern reproof{/i}.\nIt causes wracking pain and violent convulsions.\nThe target creature must make a Fortitude save or die instantly.\nA surviving creature receives a Will save to avoid further effects.\nSubjects failing the Will save are dazed and suffer a -4 penalty on saving throws for the duration of the spell.\n{b}Focus:{/b} A whip.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Magic of Faer&#251;n{/i}, 3.0 Edition" compset="Spell">
