  <thing id="iCormElfBl" name="Cormanthyrian Elfblade" description="These +1 keen longswords bear symbols of the old elven houses of Cormanthor, who were the first to develop keen magic.\n\nCaster Level: 10th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, keen edge; Market Price: 8,315 gp; Cost to Create: 4,315 gp + 320 XP.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Magic of Faer&#251;n{/i}, 3.0 Edition" compset="MagicWep" summary="+1 keen elven longsword, crafted by ancient elven houses of Cormanthor">
