  <thing id="cMWTimBody" name="Timeless Body" description="After achieving 10th level, a mystic wanderer no longer suffers ability penalties for aging (see the {i}Player&#146;s Handbook{/i}, Table 6&#150;5: Aging Effects, page 93) and cannot be magically aged. Any penalties she may have already suffered, however, remain in place. Bonuses still accrue, and the mystic wanderer still dies of old age when her time is up." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Brew potions of any 3rd level sorcere/wizard spell.">
    <usesource source="MagFaerun"/>
