  <thing id="cMWFamilia" name="Familiar" description="Beginning at 2nd level, a mystic wanderer can obtain a familiar, just as a sorcerer or wizard can. A mystic wanderer with sorcerer or wizard levels can treat her mystic wanderer levels as sorcerer or wizard levels for determining her familiar&#146;s natural armor, Intelligence, and special abilities" compset="ClSpecial" summary="Summon a familiar.">
